{"tid":929942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：聰明的小老鼠，看見這道陽光透進來的小縫，絕不會聲張","createTime":"2018-12-06T02:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T02:58:06.000Z","uid":90863,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"836ea6c403f7d80b97d12c7001d24d5013ff1f54","tid":929942,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"在一所屋子裏，牆角有一道小縫，地窖有一窩小老鼠。聰明的小老鼠，看見這道陽光透進來的小縫，絕不會聲張，吱吱大叫，奔走相告，然後放炮仗慶祝，公告地窖底下的小老鼠族群：瞧上面，有一條通往廚房的生路，一起殺過去，外面有蛋糕芝士，有社會福利。<br />\n聰明的小老鼠，會自己顧自己，悄悄的閃身潛逃出去，因為神不知、鬼不覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77194e2f27980ce4ebaddf6c6d5df274419f0ed","tid":929942,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美朝嬴國"},{"pid":"af331436ddbb4733ea6ea7fea87faa558dbda56c","tid":929942,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}